                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060219-62-defend640 t18060219-62-punish350"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
